    link: "https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-12512913/Dani-Dyer-sporty-figure-colourful-gymwear.html?ns_mchannel=rss&ns_campaign=1490&ito=1490",
    keywords: "null",
    creator: "null",
    description:
      "The former Love Island star looked fresh-faced and stylish as she left the gym after a gruelling session with her friend on Tuesday.",
    content:
      "\n\n<p>Dani Dyer, mother of three, was spotted in a vibrant exercise outfit while heading home along with a companion following a strenuous workout. The 27-year-old actress, who received twins` Summer and Star nearly four months ago with her partner Jared Bowen, is already getting back in shape with personal training sessions at the gym. The former Love Island star exuded athleticism donning teal leggings and a patterned gym top, multi-coloured. After her fitness training, she tossed on a large denim jacket while heading to her vehicle.</p>\n\n<h2>Post-Workout Essentials</h2>\n<p>The star was seen carrying her workout attire in a Nike drawstring bag slung over her shoulder, along with her other necessities encased in a £2,500 Louis Vuitton bum bag. Enjoying the satisfaction of finishing her strenuous workout, Dani seemed in a cheerful mood as she engaged in a post-workout chat with her friend. Her golden tresses were beautifully pulled back into a high ponytail, and she sported a pair of chic wide square shades.</p>\n\n<h2>Reconnecting with Fans</h2>\n<p>Meanwhile, the reality TV personality recently caught up with her followers via Instagram and apologized for her recent online absence. The mother-of-three shared a series of snapshots with a caption that said, ”I`ve been so inactive on Instagram... being a mother of three is certainly taking over.”</p>\n\n<p>Dani delighted her fans by sharing adorable photos of her twin daughters in matching pretty dresses, as well as a heartwarming picture of the twins being fed milk by their grandpa Danny Dyer. She also posted an image of her oldest child, two-year-old son Santiago, who she co-parents with her ex Sammy Kimmence, looking strikingly smart, smiling alongside his sisters and posing intently on his toy Vespa.</p>\n\n<h2>Adapting to Family Life</h2>\n<p>Just last month, Dani opened up about the changes she and her new beau Jared have experienced while transitioning into a family of five. To her fans` excitement, she revealed her struggle to find fitting clothes after having her twin girls. In an honest Q&A session on Instagram, she admitted her difficulty and made known her challenges and successes in her new life role.</p>\n\n<p>Dani reassured her fans by saying, ”Honestly, I am all good. I feel like I`m learning something new every day, and I`m avoiding putting too much pressure on myself as I did initially. Little Sants has taught me so much. I loved having a baby in the winter, much easier clothing-wise.”</p>\n\n<p>She also lauded Jarrod for being extremely helpful with the newborns following the football season. The actress confessed that her mum, Joanne Mas, provided substantial support, calling her `her rock`.</p> \n\n<p>The actress and mother-of-three concluded, ”Having Jarrod around has been amazing and lovely, as he was away in the beginning. My mum has honestly been such a great help, specifically in the early days when I couldn`t really do much!”</p>",
