      "Live Updates from Old Trafford: Outcast Antony Seen in Brazil Amid Assault Allegations, Southgate Defends Maguire Against Unwarranted Attacks",
    link: "https://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/live/article-12512367/Man-United-News-LIVE-Gareth-Southgate-slams-attacks-Harry-Maguire-new-shirt-sponsorship.html?ns_mchannel=rss&ns_campaign=1490&ito=1490",
    keywords: "null",
